Podcast Description My full interview with Liverpool centre back and Netherlands captain Virgil Van Dijk is here, brought to you by Sky Bet.
&nbsp;
Virgil opens up about growing up in Holland and slowly becoming the brilliant footballer he is today.
&nbsp;
He talks about his move to Liverpool, life at Anfield and what it’s like working with Jurgen Klopp.
&nbsp;
Plus he answers some questions from fans of the Overlap.

Podcast Description My full interview with Aston Villa manager and Liverpool legend Steven Gerrard is here, brought to you by Sky Bet.
&nbsp;
Steven tells me about how he became a manager, with Klopp giving him the u18s to manage at Liverpool.
&nbsp;
He then talks about his time with Rangers, his management style and his ambitions with Villa.
&nbsp;
We finally chat about the Chelsea game, and how he coped with the aftermath.

Podcast Description I am absolutely delighted to share this episode with you all, brought to you by Sky Bet. Frank Lampard takes me to a pub that’s close to his heart, as we tackle cocktails, starters and more in the kitchen.
We discuss how Frank moved on from Chelsea, and then how he dealt with retirement.&nbsp;
We chat all things Derby, including the infamous spy-gate… And then move on to the Chelsea job.
